OL,7,FAn organised crime group who pocketed
OL,8,Fan estimated #22 million in unpaid
OL,9,Ftaxes have been jailed.
OL,11,FAn investigation by Kent Police and
OL,12,FHMRC found the group had set up a
OL,13,Fseries of labour supply companies
OL,14,Fkeeping VAT payments from customer
OL,15,Fcompanies, that should have gone to
OL,16,FHMRC for themselves.
