OL,5,Ctaxes
OL,7,FThey also withheld financial
OL,8,Fdeductions from sub-contractors
OL,9,Fagreements that should have been given
OL,10,Fto HMRC under the Construction
OL,11,FIndustry Scheme for themselves.
OL,13,FInvestigations started after Phillip
OL,14,FBailey from Beechwood Gardens in
OL,15,FMeopham was arrested and examined for
OL,16,Ffirearms, theft and money laundering
OL,17,Foffences in April 2020.
OL,19,FOfficers began looking into the 36-
OL,20,Fyear-old's finances and established he
OL,21,Fwas a criminal accountant.
