OL,7,FPolice say Bailey was found to have
OL,8,Fset up agreements with recruited
OL,9,Fconstruction and logistics companies
OL,10,Fand started front companies and bank
OL,11,Faccounts to divert tax payments away
OL,12,Ffrom HMRC.
OL,14,FThe companies and accounts were set up
OL,15,Fin the names of front directors, not
OL,16,Fhis own, and he would pay off
OL,17,Fcomplicit company directors with a
OL,18,Fportion of the money he made from the
OL,19,Fscheme.
