OL,7,FOne of the company directors was Kevin
OL,8,FRatcliffe, 43, from Longhill Road,
OL,9,FOvingdean in Brighton who owned a
OL,10,Fconstruction company in Sussex.
OL,12,FThe authority says following Bailey's
OL,13,Farrest in 2020, Daniel Newton, 37,
OL,14,Ffrom Whitefriars Wharf in Tonbridge
OL,15,Fbecame the group's criminal accountant
OL,16,Fand carried on its activities in
OL,17,FBailey's absence.
OL,19,FOther members of the organised crime
OL,20,Fgroup who benefitted from the fraud
OL,21,Finclude:
