OL,4,Cgroup pocketing #22 million in unpaid
OL,5,Ctaxes
OL,7,FThe investigation also identified that
OL,8,Fthe group was running a profitable
OL,9,Fmoney laundering scheme for criminal
OL,10,Fassociates.
OL,12,FOver #2 million was identified as
OL,13,Fbeing linked to a large-scale drug
OL,14,Fsupply network across the southeast of
OL,15,Fthe UK.
OL,17,FThe group of seven were jailed for a
OL,18,Ftotal of around 35 years. Phillip
OL,19,FBailey was jailed for just over six
OL,20,Fyears while Daniel Newton was jailed
OL,21,Ffor more than nine years.
