OL,7,FLeading the investigation was
OL,8,FDetective Constable Dameon Shaw, who
OL,9,Fsaid: "These criminals set up and ran
OL,10,Fa large-scale operation designed to
OL,11,Fsteal VAT and CIS payments, which were
OL,12,Fthen paid out to themselves and
OL,13,Fcriminal associates.
OL,15,F"They are now paying the price for
OL,16,Ftheir actions with the sentences
OL,17,Fhanded out by the court today."
